metadata.editComments: This is the same progression as the verse and chorus, so obviously it should be described as the same mode.

The melody sounds more like it is in F# Major over an unresolved IVmaj7 chord. But the bass peddling that B does admittedly pull the tonality towards B Lydian, especially right after the first C# Minor part, where the B chord sounds fully resolved. I guess that's the charm of the song; different elements of the song are pulling the tonality in different directions.
